




{"id":11578,"date":"2022-10-24T14:18:24","date_gmt":"2022-10-24T07:18:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/?p=11578"},"modified":"2022-10-24T14:18:24","modified_gmt":"2022-10-24T07:18:24","slug":"kham-pha-tinh-nang-phan-mem-whiteboard","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/kham-pha-tinh-nang-phan-mem-whiteboard\/","title":{"rendered":"Kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m WHITEBOARD &#8211; M\u00e0n H\u00ecnh T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Gi\u00e1o D\u1ee5c INNO"},"content":{"rendered":"<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/man-hinh-tuong-tac-thong-minh-inno-itv-ka11-series\/\">M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00f4ng minh INNO<\/a> &#8211; \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c. Ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ef1c quan.<\/span><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">V\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i cho l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc th\u00f4ng minh<\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">T\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i UHD 4K v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 s\u1eafc n\u00e9t tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1eeb m\u1ecdi g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn tr\u00ean c\u00e1c k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh 55\u2033, 65\u2033, 75\u2033. 86\u2033 v\u00e0 100\u2033.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">T\u00edch h\u1ee3p b\u1ed9 x\u1eed l\u00fd v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i \u00e2m thanh\/ h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh: 3D digital comb filter and 3D noise reduction, dual 3D dynamic video progressive scan. H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Duby Vision HDR decode ATMOS\u2026<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng h\u1ed3ng ngo\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, t\u00ednh n\u0103ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 h\u1eb9n gi\u1edd t\u1eaft. Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng Miracast m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, t\u00edch h\u1ee3p nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m ti\u1ec7n \u00edch thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n cho vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-11558 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Screen-Shot-2022-09-30-at-10.59.16-530x400.png\" alt=\"- THI\u1ebeT B\u1eca HI\u1ec2N TH\u1eca,T\u01af\u01a0NG T\u00c1C TH\u00d4NG MINH\" width=\"530\" height=\"400\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Screen-Shot-2022-09-30-at-10.59.16-530x400.png 530w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Screen-Shot-2022-09-30-at-10.59.16-768x580.png 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Screen-Shot-2022-09-30-at-10.59.16-600x453.png 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Screen-Shot-2022-09-30-at-10.59.16.png 980w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">S\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a <strong>Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m WHITEBOARD t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00f4ng minh<\/strong> s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t, \u01b0u ti\u00ean t\u00ednh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i, gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ea1y d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng, nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m n\u00e0y l\u00e0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">\u0110\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i 4K UHD cho n\u00e9t thanh m\u1ea3nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m vi\u1ebft v\u1ebd hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t cao, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 vi\u1ebft \u0111\u01a1n \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m, hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng vi\u1ebft b\u00fat, v.v., h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ea3ng tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e8n \u1ea3nh, th\u00eam trang, cu\u1ed9n b\u1ea3ng b\u1eb1ng c\u1eed ch\u1ec9, ph\u00f3ng to, thu nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n v\u00f9ng, qu\u00e9t m\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb, b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 k\u00eanh n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa th\u00edch tr\u00ean giao di\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Trang b\u1ea3ng tr\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00f3ng to kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i ban \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">K\u00ednh c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00e1y n\u1ed5, \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee9ng 7 Mohs, an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">T\u00ednh n\u0103ng cho gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c\/h\u1ed9i h\u1ecdp<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">T\u00edch h\u1ee3p ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, giao di\u1ec7n ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng,&#8230;<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">T\u00edch h\u1ee3p card m\u1ea1ng k\u00e9p 2.4G \/ 5G, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi truy c\u1eadp Internet kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y v\u00e0 Wifi hotspot.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 chi\u1ebfu m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111a k\u00eanh, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n mirroring, ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh nhanh t\u1eeb xa, video, \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c, chia s\u1ebb t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u, \u1ea3nh ch\u1ee5p m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n t\u1eeb xa kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y, confidential spot projection v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng kh\u00e1c<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 120%;\">T\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0o t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-11570 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Screen-Shot-2022-10-18-at-10.22.05-647x400.jpg\" alt=\"t\u00ednh n\u0103ng Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m WHITEBOARD - M\u00e0n H\u00ecnh T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Gi\u00e1o D\u1ee5c INNO\" width=\"647\" height=\"400\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Screen-Shot-2022-10-18-at-10.22.05-647x400.jpg 647w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Screen-Shot-2022-10-18-at-10.22.05-768x475.jpg 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Screen-Shot-2022-10-18-at-10.22.05-600x371.jpg 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Screen-Shot-2022-10-18-at-10.22.05.jpg 980w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 647px) 100vw, 647px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, <strong>Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m WHITEBOARD\u00a0<\/strong>c\u00f3 c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng:<\/span><\/h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><strong>Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd t\u1eadp tin<\/strong><\/span><\/h4>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Ph\u00e2n ra c\u00e1c th\u01b0 m\u1ee5c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng gi\u00fap gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00e1c t\u1eadp tin<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm, ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, \u00e2m thanh, video, t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, sao ch\u00e9p, di chuy\u1ec3n, x\u00f3a, \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00ean th\u01b0 m\u1ee5c \u2026<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp t\u1eadp tin theo t\u00ean, lo\u1ea1i, ng\u00e0y, k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc, \u2026\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><strong>Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00f3i (Anti-glare):<\/strong> Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><strong>Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng anti-light<\/strong>: Ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n s\u1ef1 xu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea5p g\u00e2y ra trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<blockquote><p>Ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c thao t\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m WHITEBOARD &#8211; M\u00e0n H\u00ecnh T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Th\u00f4ng Minh c\u1ee7a INNOho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ea1y t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi M\u00e0n H\u00ecnh T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Th\u00f4ng Minh, C\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng minh kh\u00e1c,h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay INNO t\u1ea1i fanpage\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/innovietnam\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/a> ho\u1eb7c Hotline: 0926 557 757\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chi ti\u1ebft nh\u00e9!<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00f4ng minh INNO &#8211; \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c. Ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ef1c quan. V\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u